commentary: Rampaul to Umar Akmal, OUT What a sharp lovely lifting snorter! Rampaul has taken out Umar Akmal with a beauty. It screamed up at Umar who hopped but jumped right into more trouble. he would have been better off trying to leave it but it's easier said than done of course. He jumped to try get on top of the bounce but it kept climbing. Trouble. He tried to sway away at the last instant. Too late. The ball clipped the edge and flew to the keeper.

commentary: Bishoo to Hammad Azam, OUT Given out lbw though there was an inside edge. It landed full on a length around middle and began to turn towards middle and off. Enter Shahid Afridi.

commentary: Bishoo to Mohammad Salman, OUT If only he had run properly last ball, he wouldn't have been on strike this delivery to face this absolute gem! The deadly flipper! It landed on a length, or perhaps back of a length,  around the off stump line and Salman thought, ok let me cut. Fatal mistake. The ball skidded on quickly and straight towards the off stump before he could get the bat down. Whoosh! Clatter!
